title: 10 Chess Books - August 2016 (gnv64)
description:
A collection of 10 chess books in PDF and ePUB formats:

01. Catalog of Chess Mistakes by Andrew Soltis
02. Chess for You and Me by Milton Hanauer
03. Chessboard Magic by Irving Chernev
04. Frank Marshall, United States Chess Champion by Andrew Soltis
05. Solving in Style by John Nunn
06. The Art of the Checkmate by Georges Renaud, Victor Kahn
07. The Ultimate Chess Puzzle Book by John Emms
08. The Ultimate Chess Strategy Book 1 by Alfonso Romero, Amador Gonzalez de la Nava
09. Liquidation on the Chess Board - Mastering the Transition into the Pawn Ending
10. Sacrifice and Initiative in Chess by Ivan Sokolov
